summary: Cute female Nord just leaving Helgen, with the Stormcloak warrior.
descriptionHtml:
[b][color=#57a2e5]Pretty Much:[/color]
[color=black]====[/color][/b]
Cute female Nord just leaving Helgen, with the Stormcloak warrior.

[b][color=#57a2e5]Save File:[/color]
[color=black]====[/color][/b]
Just leaving the cave from Helgen with the Stormcloak warrior.

[b][color=#57a2e5]Description:[/color]
[color=black]====[/color][/b]
Posted purely for those who like the look of her and would like to use it as their own character. If you want to start from the tutorial, check out one of the guides on Skyrim Nexus that tell you how to do so with the character I\'ve created.

[b][color=#57a2e5]Character Mods Used:[/color]
[color=black]====[/color][/b]
All of Xenius\' brilliant character detail mods.

[b][color=#57a2e5]Other Saves:[/color]
[color=black]====[/color][/b]
[url=http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=1835]Yet Another Female Nord[/url]
My favourite of the bunch.
[url=http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=1683]Another Female Orc[/url]
The only female Orc I\'ve created that looks decent to good at all times.
